{"tid":1613780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"實用救生工具介紹----紅色錘仔","createTime":"2019-10-02T15:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:44:14.000Z","uid":193224,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"79962f537149eaae091637dd90d8be522f0280a4","tid":1613780,"uid":193224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"代朋友post <br />\n我朋友想推薦一樣工具比大家，就係巴士上層嘅紅色錘仔。個隻錘仔唔單止輕便仲容易用，幾下就可以打爛玻璃。佢建議大家去買翻個旁身。千奇唔好借/拎巴士個d ，唔好搞巴士。香港人甘有錢要就自己買，amazon有得買。<br />\n<br />\n利申，係教導大家使用工具協助自己在附近有玻璃圍困個陣逃生。千奇唔好拎黨鐵玻璃來試下work唔work。本人反對一切形式暴力行為。"},{"pid":"559f0ca790bde08de8e1ffa375b92bb351abcb1f","tid":1613780,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c479954ded920aaf4c8f6c24bec167e599c3645","tid":1613780,"uid":67049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"收到"},{"pid":"d77f238a2756a7487ebd3cb853564bac2b7bfa72","tid":1613780,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />反對暴力"}]}